name: The Black Cat
title: Main Hall
creator: spookyghostboo
description: The Black Cat is an [Oculus Quest](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oculus_Quest) enabled world featuring a restaurant, two bars, two stages and many lounging areas. The map is fairly small but roomy enough that its possible to move to a private areas when needed. It has separate bathrooms for male and female visitors. The world has a mirror.
